videos.description: Cam Reddish takes the defensive rebound and finishes the fast break with the salm.
videos.headline: Reddish takes it coast to coast for the slam

videos.description: Louisville's Jordan Nwora runs up to steal the ball from Duke's RJ Barrett and dunks it at the other end.
videos.headline: Nwora swipes Barrett for the fast-break dunk

videos.description: Darius Perry reaches back and floats the ball in with one hand to extend Louisville's lead to 38-29 at the half.
videos.headline: Perry sinks one-handed buzzer-beater to end first half

videos.description: Duke's Jack White passes on the 3-pointer and gets called for the charge on the drive to the basket.
videos.headline: White gets called for the charge

videos.description: Duke's Zion Williamson sends the driving layup and gets the rebound on the follow up.
videos.headline: Zion blocks a shot at the rim

videos.description: Zion Williamson makes the great defensive play and RJ Barrett completes the fast break with a Eurostep finish.
videos.headline: Barrett finishes Zion steal with a smooth Eurostep

videos.description: Zion Williamson pushes the fast break and finishes at the rim while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Zion powers through for the and-1 bucket

videos.description: RJ Barrett hits Cam Reddish with a between-the-legs pass for a game-tying 3-pointer after Duke at one point trailed Louisville by 23.
videos.headline: Barrett between-the-legs dish to Reddish for game-tying 3

videos.description: Louisville's Christen Cunningham misses the jumper to tie the game and Duke finishes a 23-point comeback with a 71-69 win.
videos.headline: Louisville get can't game in final seconds as Duke holds on

videos.description: Zion Williamson talks postgame about Duke's comeback and how Coach K kept the Blue Devils in the game.
videos.headline: Zion: Coach K said, 'I don't coach losers. I coach winners'

videos.description: Zion Williamson records a double-double with 27 points and 12 rebounds as he leads Duke to a 71-69 comeback win.
